# Civic & Economic Literacy Quiz -- EquiQuiz

An interactive quiz application that tests your knowledge of civic and economic concepts with beautiful data visualization.

## Features

- ðŸŽ¯ Interactive multiple-choice questions
- ðŸ“Š Score tracking with visual feedback
